    <h2>The Land of Tender Coconuts</h2>
    <h3>Explore, Experience, Enjoy!</h3>

    <!-- Descriptive Paragraphs -->
    <p>Tiptur is a small town in Karnataka, India, famous for its tender coconuts, serene landscapes, and vibrant culture. Nestled in the southern part of the state, it offers a slice of rural charm combined with modernity.</p>

    <!-- Unordered List -->
    <h2>Highlights of Tiptur:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Delicious and fresh tender coconuts</li>
        <li>Traditional silk weaving industry</li>
        <li>Beautiful temples and heritage sites</li>
    </ul>

